dc_description_s: Mounted cover title. Title on map: Fukui-ken zenzu. Copperplate print. In Japanese. Oriented with north to the lower left. Relief shown by hachures. Includes 9 insets and distance chart. Includes preface and legend. Engraved by Kyōsendō. 1 map: col.; 81 x 114 cm., folded in cover 24 x 16 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
